SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 4162
A bill to amend 1979 PA 94, entitled
"The state school aid act of 1979,"
by amending sections 11, 20, 22a, 22b, 31aa, 51a, 51c, 51d, 51e,
53a, 54, 147a, 147c, and 147e (MCL 388.1611, 388.1620, 388.1622a,
388.1622b, 388.1631aa, 388.1651a, 388.1651c, 388.1651d, 388.1651e,
388.1653a, 388.1654, 388.1747a, 388.1747c, and 388.1747e), sections
11 and 31aa as amended by 2024 PA 148 and sections 20, 22a, 22b,
51a, 51c, 51d, 51e, 53a, 54, 147a, 147c, and 147e as amended by
2024 PA 120, and by adding section 201i.
